dc_title_s: Silvio Valenti Tit. S. Callix Presb. S.R.E. Card. Camerario Benedicti XIV P.M. Administro Urbis ichnographiam
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. "35, 36." Shows names of streets, buildings, plazas, churches, drainage, and other points of interest. Includes index. From: Geschichte der Stadt Rom / von Alfred von Reumont. Berlin : Verlag der königlichen geheimen Ober-Hofbuchdruckerei, R.v. Decker, 1867-1870. Facsimile of map originally published in Rome in 1748.
